text: Moolaadé ("magical protection") is a 2004 Senegalese Burkinabé Moroccan Tunisian Cameroonian French drama movie directed by Ousmane Sembène and starring Fatoumata Coulibaly, Maïmouna Hélène Diarra, Salimata Traore, Dominique T.
